title: Gary Owen Stops By To Rep Who Dey Nation!!!
description:
Jalen & Jacoby kick off Super Bowl Week with comedian and Bengals fan Gary Owen!!! Plus the guys dive into the Nets 8-game losing streak, what’s going on with James Harden, Joel Embiid’s MVP chances, are Cavs legit contenders in East, Caitlin Clark's crazy 46-point game against Michigan and much more.
